% Basic Skolemization test: simple goal with variables
% Goal P(x) is implicitly universally quantified: ∀x P(x)
% Negation: ∃x ¬P(x)
% Skolemization: ¬P(c1) where c1 is a fresh Skolem constant
%
% Expected: the denied goal should be -P(c1), NOT -P(x)

formulas(sos).
  P(a).
  P(b).
  a != b.
end_of_list.

formulas(goals).
  P(x).
end_of_list.
